question: List all boardgames by GMT.
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:publisher res:GMT_Games }

question: Who developed Skype?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Skype dbo:developer ?uri. }

question: Which people were born in Heraklion?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type onto:Person ; onto:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heraklion>. }

question: Which airports does Air China serve?

question: Give me all actors starring in movies directed by and starring William Shatner.
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?x dbo:director res:William_Shatner ; dbo:starring res:William_Shatner { ?x dbo:starring ?uri } UNION { ?x dbp:starring ?uri } }

question: Which movies starring Brad Pitt were directed by Guy Ritchie?

question: Which organizations were founded in 1950?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Organisation { ?uri dbo:formationYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:foundation ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:formation ?date } FILTER regex(?date, "^1950") }
